  "page": "The Chronicles of Longsister",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>The Chronicles of Longsister</b></i> discusses the history of <a href=\"/index.php/Longsister\" title=\"Longsister\">Longsister</a>, one of the islands of the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vale\">Vale</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Bite\" title=\"Bite\">Bite</a>. Its content includes the <a href=\"/index.php/Rape_of_the_Three_Sisters\" title=\"Rape of the Three Sisters\">Rape of the Three Sisters</a>, describing how <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">northmen</a> committed horrors upon <a href=\"/index.php/Sistermen\" title=\"Sistermen\">Sistermen</a>, leading to the <a href=\"/index.php/War_Across_the_Water\" title=\"War Across the Water\">War Across the Water</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Chronicles_of_Longsister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Vale.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404212255\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCP